Kya hota hai maa hone ka ehsaas,
Ye tune mujhe samjhaya hai,
Mere aansuon mein bhi khushi dhoondh lana,
Ye toh tune hi mujhe sikhaya hai.
Tune chuna hai mujhe, banaya apna ghar,
Teri muskurahat meri duaon ka sabab bani,
Teri har saans meri zindagi ka geet bani.
Har pal tere saath mein maa hone ka garv hai,
Teri har khushi mein mera har armaan  hai,
Tujh mein hi toh meri poori duniya basi hai,
Tere hone se hi meri pehchaan MAA bani hai.
